ke, 'OK, I am going to be careful, I am going to follow the same protocol every time and then I am going to avoid (the pitfalls)' and that's all you can do.\\\"\", \"from\": 5492, \"to\": 5665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same protocol\", \"from\": 5564, \"to\": 5581}, {\"ngram\": \"(the pitfalls\", \"from\": 5622, \"to\": 5635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. Classic this weekend inConnecticut.\", \"from\": 5667, \"to\": 5711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The U.S. Classic\", \"from\": 5667, \"to\": 5683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. Championships later this month.\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The U.S. Championships\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Trials in late June.\", \"from\": 5753, \"to\": 5785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5757, \"end\": 5771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794952675, \"rank\": 0.038961038961052005, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"late June\", \"from\": 5775, \"to\": 5784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One turn, one routine, one rotation, one meet at a time.\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 5842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One turn\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 5794}, {\"ngram\": \"one routine\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5807}, {\"ngram\": \"one rotation\", \"from\": 5809, \"to\": 5821}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 5835, \"to\": 5841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With all the tools - including her therapist - at the ready.\", \"from\": 5843, \"to\": 5903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the tools\", \"from\": 5848, \"to\": 5861}, {\"ngram\": \"her therapist\", \"from\": 5874, \"to\": 